#: ../../../system/s390x/pcidevices.rst:2
msgid "PCI devices on s390x"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../system/s390x/pcidevices.rst:4
msgid ""
"PCI devices on s390x work differently than on other architectures and need "
"to be configured in a slightly different way."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../system/s390x/pcidevices.rst:7
msgid ""
"Every PCI device is linked with an additional ``zpci`` device. While the "
"``zpci`` device will be autogenerated if not specified, it is recommended to "
"specify it explicitly so that you can pass s390-specific PCI configuration."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../system/s390x/pcidevices.rst:12
msgid ""
"For example, in order to pass a PCI device ``0000:00:00.0`` through to the "
"guest, you would specify::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../system/s390x/pcidevices.rst:15
msgid ""
"qemu-system-s390x ... \\\n"
"                  -device zpci,uid=1,fid=0,target=hostdev0,id=zpci1 \\\n"
"                  -device vfio-pci,host=0000:00:00.0,id=hostdev0"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../system/s390x/pcidevices.rst:19
msgid ""
"Here, the zpci device is joined with the PCI device via the ``target`` "
"property."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../system/s390x/pcidevices.rst:21
msgid ""
"Note that we don't set bus, slot or function here for the guest as is common "
"in other PCI implementations. Topology information is not available on "
"s390x, and the guest will not see any of the bus, slot or function "
"information specified on the command line."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../system/s390x/pcidevices.rst:26
msgid ""
"Instead, ``uid`` and ``fid`` determine how the device is presented to the "
"guest operating system."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../system/s390x/pcidevices.rst:29
msgid ""
"In case of Linux, ``uid`` will be used in the ``domain`` part of the PCI "
"identifier, and ``fid`` identifies the physical slot, i.e.::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../system/s390x/pcidevices.rst:32
msgid ""
"qemu-system-s390x ... \\\n"
"                  -device zpci,uid=7,fid=8,target=hostdev0,id=zpci1 \\\n"
"                  ..."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../system/s390x/pcidevices.rst:36
msgid "will be presented in the guest as::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../system/s390x/pcidevices.rst:38
msgid ""
"# lspci -v\n"
"0007:00:00.0 ...\n"
"Physical Slot: 00000008\n"
"..."
msgstr ""
